---
title: Pesto Risoni & Roasted Pumpkin with Lemon–Chilli Pangrattato & Feta
description: Risoni – the clever pasta that looks like rice – is the ideal ingredient in this warm bowl. With baby spinach and leek, this dinner filled with goodness gets the welcome addition of feta and basil pesto to really raise the flavour stakes.

*Unfortunately, this week's green beans were in short supply, so we've replaced them with leek. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pesto-roast-pumpkin-fetta-risoni-5794ad59.jpg
